      "content": "i see. so it was mostly about physical measurements. but there were also the early IQ tests, right? i remember reading that those were used to \"prove\" these differences too. can u explain how those tests were structured and what kind of results they typically showed for different racial groups? i want to make sure my essay captures how they used these standardized metrics to provide a layer of \"scientific\" legitimacy to the whole idea of racial hierarchy.",
